import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter,Routes,Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import App from './App'

const MainApp = () => {
  return (
    <>
    < BrowserRouter>
    
    <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<App/>}/>
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
    </>
  )
}

export default MainApp
